history.content:
Join SWE for our Winter SWElebration where we'll be recapping the semester, announcing our new officers, and engaging in holiday festivities. While we may have food at the event, it will not be enough for dinner, so please make sure to eat afterwards. If you also attended GM3 or EWI and have yet to pick up your swag, you can pick up your swag at the event! Make sure to dress in your favorite ugly sweater and RSVP at our facebook link :D

The online zoom option will primarily be for announcements only, so please join us in-person if you'd like to engage in our winter festivities.

-EVENT DETAILS-
Date: Thursday 12/2
Time: 5-6:30 PM
Location: 290 HMMB
Zoom Link: https://tinyurl.com/ucbswefa21gm4
